{"about_the_game":"A physics-based platformer without a jump button. Walk, jump, climb and parkour by directly controlling each leg of a confused baby robot. Go from a glitching toddler to a somersaulting acrobat in the story mode, or share a multi-legged robot with your friends for extra chaos!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1461930/extras/subheader_01.png?t=1720196909\" /><br><br>Robotry! is played with a gamepad. Each analog stick controls one leg of your robot. The body of the robot balances itself automatically. You can walk by taking alternating steps, or jump by pushing against the ground. Grabbing, throwing, kicking, climbing and cranking are also all built upon direct physics-based control.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1461930/extras/RopeSwing_down2_rounded.gif?t=1720196909\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1461930/extras/subheader_02.png?t=1720196909\" /><br><br>Help the merry orange astronauts do cool science experiments on different planets as you chuck yourself around the cosmos! Walk, run, skip, hop and tumble through the campaign in single player or join forces with a friend or two!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1461930/extras/HUB_hop_rounded.gif?t=1720196909\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1461930/extras/subheader_03.png?t=1720196909\" /><br><br>Who's the most elegant robo pilot? After you've finished the campaign, it's time to settle this in various multiplayer minigames playable with up to 4 players. Game modes include:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Volleyball<br></li><li> Bounce The Pengu<br></li><li> Waypoint Chase<br></li><li> Gem Hunt</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1461930/extras/steam_snow_rounded.gif?t=1720196909\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1461930/extras/subheader_04.png?t=1720196909\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The main story is available as both single player and local co-op.<br></li><li>You can play the co-op mode with multiple robots, or players can control different legs of the same robot!<br></li><li>Throw around heebos, they don\u2019t mind!<br></li><li>Customize your robots!<br></li><li>Collect secrets and explore the HUB, your sandbox-like spaceship playground!</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1461930/extras/Boulder_zone_rounded.gif?t=1720196909\" /><br><br>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Out of the Basement","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1461930/9a7d6aa5aa4fba06589c2be56daf99c10ecce7e4.jpg"},{"name":"Go Hyper!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1461930/62620d1d3e97f9e4d740faa2dfc073862e7c2c8f.jpg"},{"name":"Plentiful Juice","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1461930/fe0ee1513076174d20894f60ab6b0fa497bf21f4.jpg"},{"name":"Spa Day","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1461930/d8f51c22be3a05264c6026612637919eeecbbbe5.jpg"},{"name":"Intended Intendent","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1461930/bb8bb0a658af01fd6de3ea2c11c35144a8112c82.jpg"},{"name":"Master of Gravity","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1461930/865fa6ea45a9374944246e9b92601e515069739f.jpg"},{"name":"Captain, Wake Up!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1461930/f239a1a0a164503538fa5f4b59c9fc925eb1f6e5.jpg"},{"name":"No Time F